snippet.title: Cartoon Network Punch Time Explosion Trailer
snippet.description: Here is a trailer I put together for Cartoon Networks "Punch Time Explosion". It contains 5 seperate clips of seperate gameplay videos put together of Dexter, Bubbles, Buttercup, Chowder and Blossom. Crave Games today announced that it has entered into an agreement with Cartoon Network Enterprises (CNE), the global licensing and merchandising arm of the television network, to develop and produce Cartoon Network Punch Time Explosion for the Nintendo 3DS™ entertainment system available in May 2011.  The game will also be released for the Xbox 360®video game and entertainment system from Microsoft, Nintendo Wii™ and the PlayStation®3 computer entertainment system during the 2011 holiday season.
